{"tid":713753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[復仇者聯盟] 賓館清潔女工不忿被炒 持刀找晦氣被打傷","createTime":"2018-06-23T05:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T15:06:53.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ddbf8b650729c3e1314ac4908558f33484219af8","tid":713753,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T05:50:40.000Z","msg":"早上10時40分，一名年約40歲女子，被途人發現在油麻地砵蘭街112號路邊，左手受傷流血，身旁有一把生果刀，於是報警，由救護員替她包紥，然後送院。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查得悉，女傷者是現場一間賓館的清潔女工，較早前被解僱。今早她手持生果刀到來找晦氣，但被打退，混亂中亦被刀割傷手，於是走落樓求救。警方以涉嫌襲擊拘捕賓館一名職員，而女傷者亦涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器被捕。"},{"pid":"36dadcaa9f31b2fa08244b97b0080978ec46143b","tid":713753,"uid":36296,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T05:52:56.000Z","msg":"東家唔打打東家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57467b483e62cbb39a39f244877b2045d0d695f7","tid":713753,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"36dadcaa9f31b2fa08244b97b0080978ec46143b","tid":713753,"uid":36296,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T05:52:56.000Z","msg":"東家唔打打東家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T05:53:42.000Z","msg":"好文采"},{"pid":"6b5b41d1614cf44a024a298ec60d440ed483a46e","tid":713753,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:46:06.000Z","msg":"肯定又係支那大嬸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2842eb8b2698822f05eaa8b0018aa1bf9f91f3","tid":713753,"uid":173058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"57467b483e62cbb39a39f244877b2045d0d695f7","tid":713753,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"36dadcaa9f31b2fa08244b97b0080978ec46143b","tid":713753,"uid":36296,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T05:52:56.000Z","msg":"東家唔打打東家<i